graph TB
    subgraph "Llama Stack Kubernetes Operator"
        Controller[Operator Controller Manager<br/>Deployment]
        LLSDController[LlamaStackDistribution Controller<br/>Go Controller]
        Kustomize[Kustomize Transformer<br/>Internal Library]
        DistResolver[Distribution Resolver<br/>Internal Component]
        NetPolicy[Network Policy Manager<br/>Internal Component]
        Storage[Storage Provisioner<br/>Internal Component]

        Controller -->|watches CRDs| LLSDController
        LLSDController -->|uses| Kustomize
        LLSDController -->|uses| DistResolver
        LLSDController -->|creates| NetPolicy
        LLSDController -->|creates| Storage
    end

    subgraph "Managed Resources"
        LLSDCR[LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>llamastack.io/v1alpha1]
        Deployment[Llama Stack Server Deployment<br/>Managed Deployment]
        Service[Llama Stack Service<br/>ClusterIP 8321/TCP]
        PVC[PersistentVolumeClaim<br/>Model Storage]
        NP[NetworkPolicy<br/>Ingress Restrictions]
        SA[ServiceAccount<br/>RBAC Permissions]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        Registry[Container Registry<br/>quay.io 443/TCP]
    end

    subgraph "Inference Providers"
        Ollama[Ollama Server<br/>11434/TCP HTTP]
        vLLM[vLLM Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP]
        TGI[TGI Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
        HF[HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    User[User/CI] -->|creates| LLSDCR
    LLSDCR -->|watched by| LLSDController

    LLSDController -->|creates/manages| Deployment
    LLSDController -->|creates| Service
    LLSDController -->|creates| PVC
    LLSDController -->|creates| NP
    LLSDController -->|creates| SA

    Controller -->|watches/updates| K8sAPI
    Controller -->|exposes metrics| Prometheus

    Deployment -->|pulls from| Registry
    Deployment -->|connects to| Ollama
    Deployment -->|connects to| vLLM
    Deployment -->|connects to| TGI
    Deployment -->|downloads models| HF

    Deployment -->|uses| PVC
    Service -->|routes to| Deployment

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style LLSDController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style LLSDCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Deployment fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Ollama fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style vLLM fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style TGI fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
